              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8 col-lg-4">
        <div class="fdb-box">
          <div class="row no-gutters align-items-center">
            <div class="col-3">
              <img alt="image" class="img-fluid rounded" src="<%=ShootType.find_by(id:18).avatar_url(:mini) %>">
            </div>
            <div class="col-8 ml-auto">
              <p class="text-right">
                <strong> مجتبی خداوردیان </strong><br>
